The movie starts with Five friends Robert, Hutch,&nbsp;
Phil, Dom, and Luke planning a group vacation.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:18.560
They all come up with different ideas of going&nbsp;
to Amsterdam, Berlin, Belgium, etc., when Robert&nbsp;&nbsp;

