No one was particularly pleased with the journey,&nbsp;
but they did it anyway for Rob. Hutch suggests&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:29.920
doing a little bit more hiking to make the most of&nbsp;
their trip, but Luke refuses and says it's enough&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:29.920 --> 00:01:35.120
for me. They are heading back to the lodge when&nbsp;
Dom falls and gets his ankle twisted. They decide&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:40.000
to take a shorter passage through the forest.&nbsp;
Hutch gets excited about the off-trail hiking.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:44.240
After the walk some distance, Luke suggests&nbsp;
leaving Phil and Dom behind to get some help.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:49.760
Dom immediately rejects the idea and says he can&nbsp;
walk if they take the quicker route. They continue&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:53.920
to walk through the forest, taking pictures,&nbsp;
talking, being unaware of what strange thing they&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:58.080
have gotten themselves in. While they are moving&nbsp;
between the trees, Phil says that this forest is&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:58.080 --> 00:02:02.880
awkwardly quiet, but Dom shuts his thoughts by&nbsp;
saying that the trees absorb sound, making the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:05.680
place calm and nothing unusual. After walking some&nbsp;
distance, they decide to get some rest. They start&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:10.000
again and are discussing their university life&nbsp;
when they see blood dripping down from a tree.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:14.640
A body ripped open and gutted is hanging from a&nbsp;
tree. They also saw some strange symbols on the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:18.080
tree. The group members become suspicious&nbsp;
and start making guesses about why someone&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:18.080 --> 00:02:22.560
would hang a body from the tree like this. The&nbsp;
blood was still fresh, so they kept moving.&nbsp;

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:26.720
It starts raining, and they have to look for&nbsp;
shelter. The pals see a house from some distance&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:26.720 --> 00:02:30.880
and decide to check it out. Dom suggests leaving&nbsp;
and going from that place, but others break into&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:30.880 --> 00:02:34.880
the house as they cannot stay out in the rain.&nbsp;
While they all are trying to settle, Luke hears&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:34.880 --> 00:02:38.711
some distorted voices coming from outside. He asks&nbsp;
his friends if they heard any voice coming from&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:38.711 --> 00:02:42.080
outside, but they all tell him they didn't. They&nbsp;
find some necklaces with the same symbols they&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:47.120
saw outside, in the abandoned house. They want to&nbsp;
start a fire in that place, so they ask Phil to go&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:51.920
up and look for some wood. There is total darkness&nbsp;
up the staircase. Phil uses his torch to open the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:56.880
door and yells at everyone to leave after seeing&nbsp;
what is inside. Everyone comes to see why Phil got&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:56.880 --> 00:03:02.960
upset. A statue made of twigs of a decapitated&nbsp;
human torso with antlers for hands was hanging&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:07.440
in the room. Phil says it was something related to&nbsp;
witchcraft. Others are not bothered by that thing,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:07.440 --> 00:03:11.280
so they go down to get the fire started.
They discuss that Pagans and Nordic people&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:15.280
may have lived in this place because who else&nbsp;
can think to live in the middle of nowhere.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:19.600
Hutch tries to make his friends comfortable by&nbsp;
saying that we will be okay as we have food and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:19.600 --> 00:03:24.400
supplies for now. They all talk for some time&nbsp;
and then go to sleep. Soft knocking and growling&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:24.400 --> 00:03:29.120
sound keeps coming up from the darkness outside.&nbsp;
Luke wakes up from his sleep. A light appears to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:33.280
come from outside the window. He follows the&nbsp;
light, taking him to the memory where Robert&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:37.760
died in the shop. He comes back to reality from&nbsp;
his nightmare and finds himself standing outside&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:41.840
the house with drops of blood on his shirt. He&nbsp;
finds punctured wounds on his chest. Hutch also&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:46.160
wakes up screaming. Luke goes inside and sees&nbsp;
everyone panicked and scared by the nightmares&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:46.160 --> 00:03:51.200
they just had. Phil is missing. They go upstairs&nbsp;
to check for him, where they find him naked,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:55.600
praying to the statue. Everyone gets ready to go,&nbsp;
and no one talks about what has just happened.&nbsp;

00:03:55.600 --> 00:03:59.520
Luke is standing by a tree, looking at the&nbsp;
symbols. Others say that this is a warning&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:03:59.520 --> 00:04:03.600
for them. Dom spots a path and asks his friends&nbsp;
to follow him down it. While they are moving,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:03.600 --> 00:04:08.400
Phil asks to discuss what just happened to them.&nbsp;
Hutch says it was just a bad dream, a nightmare,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:12.240
and they just spooked because of it. Nothing else&nbsp;
happened. Phil continued insisting that something&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:17.440
was there. Something made him go naked and pray&nbsp;
to that statue. Luke becomes angry at Phil saying&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:17.440 --> 00:04:21.280
it’s all non-sense and tells him that listen to&nbsp;
what he’s are saying. Dom is determined to get&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:21.280 --> 00:04:26.320
out of that place. After some time, Dom gets tired&nbsp;
and decides to rest for a while. The others become&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:30.800
angry at him for slowing them down. They tell him&nbsp;
to bear the pain and move faster, or they will&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:30.800 --> 00:04:35.280
never get out of that place. Dom does not respond&nbsp;
to them and doesn’t move. Luke decides to go and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:39.440
see how far they have to go. He is standing in&nbsp;
