00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:44.080
on his chest, when he hears low growls. Luke sees&nbsp;
a creature in the woods and runs back to tell his&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:44.080 --> 00:04:48.480
friends about it. He explains to them there is&nbsp;
something big in the woods. No one seems to be&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:52.160
moved by this, so Luke shows his wounds to them&nbsp;
and asks them if there is no one, then how did he&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:56.560
get those wounds. Dom denies everything he is&nbsp;
saying and argues with Luke. Dom says to him&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:56.560 --> 00:05:00.800
that we are here because of you. Luke comes back&nbsp;
at him to which Dom says, where was this fight&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:00.800 --> 00:05:05.680
when Robert was dying in front of you. Luke takes&nbsp;
his backpack and leaves when Dom says that robbers&nbsp;&nbsp;

