00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:21.040
is disturbed by what Dom had said, and so he asks&nbsp;
Hutch that it was, is his fault that he didn't&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:24.960
stand up to the robbers when Rob died? Hutch does&nbsp;
not answer. They continue walking without saying&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:29.120
anything. While they are walking, they see some&nbsp;
fabric buried in the ground. They pull that thing&nbsp;&nbsp;

