00:05:35.200 --> 00:05:40.000
tension and says, we will not end up like these&nbsp;
people. People will come looking for us as we have&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:45.040
registered in the lodge. Hutch takes Luke to a&nbsp;
corner and says that Phil is not looking good and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:49.440
Dom is also suffering because of his knee. He is&nbsp;
strong, so he should go and look for help in the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:53.200
morning. He will stay with the two friends. The&nbsp;
sound of branches snapping and growling continues.&nbsp;&nbsp;

