Luke is in his tent when he hears roaring and&nbsp;
screeching. He unzips the tent and sneaks out&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:02.800
to take a look. He’s once again taken to his&nbsp;
memory of the day Robert was killed. He hears&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:07.440
someone calling him a coward and wakes up from the&nbsp;
dream upon hearing Phil scream. When he inspects&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:12.480
the situation, he finds out that Hutch is missing&nbsp;
and that Phil saw a creature, shadows taking him.&nbsp;

00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:16.560
They hear Hutch’s screams coming from a distance.&nbsp;
Everyone is scared, but they gather the courage&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:20.640
to go and find Hutch. They follow the steps&nbsp;
in the mud, and after covering some distance,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:20.640 --> 00:06:24.800
they find him ripped open, hanging from a tree.&nbsp;
They take him down, and everyone is crying about&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:29.200
losing another friend. Luke says to go because&nbsp;
the creature that did this will be coming back,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:35.040
but Dom insists on giving Hutch a proper burial.&nbsp;
Dom argues on this with Luke. He says to keep his&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:35.040 --> 00:06:38.880
voice down. He tries to calm them by saying&nbsp;
that I have a knife, and we know the path&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:43.360
Hutch told us so we can safely get out of the&nbsp;
forest. They keep going. They stop to drink water&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:47.360
when they see foot prints in the mud. Dom suggests&nbsp;
that it means there are people out there. Luke&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:52.400
decides not to follow them and continues going to&nbsp;
Southwest. Everyone is disturbed by what happened,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:55.760
but Luke tells them that they are far&nbsp;
from that house now and are somehow safe.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:55.760 --> 00:07:00.880
Dom stops to gasp some air. Luke moves to get a&nbsp;
look at where they have reached. He sees the end&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:04.720
and comes back to tell his friends about it. Luke&nbsp;
finds out that the creature has attacked Phil and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:08.480
that his friends are not there. Luke again&nbsp;
goes into his nightmare, and when he snaps&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:12.800
back into reality, he starts looking for his&nbsp;
friends. Luke finds Dom hiding behind a tree,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:17.040
scared to death. Dom says he doesn't know what&nbsp;
happened, but they figured out that the creature&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:17.040 --> 00:07:21.760
was hunting them. Luke tells him that he has found&nbsp;
a way out and will not let anything happen to Dom.&nbsp;

00:07:21.760 --> 00:07:25.840
The sound of the branches snapping continues in&nbsp;
the darkness. Luke tells Dom that he will count&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:29.920
down from 3, and then they will run as fast as&nbsp;
possible. The heavy footsteps start to follow&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:29.920 --> 00:07:33.840
them, and the growling grows louder. They spot the&nbsp;
creature and run from it. After wandering through&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:33.840 --> 00:07:37.840
the forest for a while they find Phil's body&nbsp;
hanging from a tree. They continue running through&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:37.840 --> 00:07:41.440
the forest as the creature seemingly follows&nbsp;
them, they see a house, and when they enter it,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:42.080 --> 00:07:45.120
the radio is playing, and they see some&nbsp;
people in there. They are knocked out,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:45.120 --> 00:07:48.960
and when they wake up, they find themselves&nbsp;
chained in a cellar. Luke tries to see out&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:48.960 --> 00:07:52.240
from an opening in the wooden wall and sees&nbsp;
some people. They plan to cut the rope with&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:56.720
the glass of the bottle lying on the table when&nbsp;
two men and one woman enter the room. The woman&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:56.720 --> 00:08:00.640
offers Luke some water and sees the wounds&nbsp;
on his chest. She also shows him the ones&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:00.640 --> 00:08:04.960
on her. She then goes to Dom but doesn't offer&nbsp;
him water. Instead, she says something in an&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:09.520
unknown language, and the man takes Dom outside&nbsp;
up the stairs. Luke hears thudding, growling,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:14.800
and crying. A girl visits Luke and says that the&nbsp;
people will prepare for the sacrifice ritual soon.&nbsp;

00:08:14.800 --> 00:08:19.280
After some time, they bring Dom back to the&nbsp;
cellar. He is not in good shape and is bleeding.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:19.280 --> 00:08:24.080
Luke asks him if he’s okay. Dom starts telling&nbsp;
him about the nightmare he saw in that house. Dom&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:28.800
says that he saw these people offering him to that&nbsp;
creature, and at the end, he saw his wife, Gayle.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:33.600
He says I will die here, but you have to live.&nbsp;
Burn the place down when you leave it and tell my&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:33.600 --> 00:08:38.480
wife that I tried to get back to her. People then&nbsp;
take Dom for the sacrifice as Luke looks through&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:38.480 --> 00:08:43.360
the opening. The group chants meanwhile Luke&nbsp;
tries to get the cuffs off his hands. Dom yells&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:47.760
at the people, “go on, what are you waiting for&nbsp;
now”. The creature appears from behind the trees,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:51.840
and people start bowing to him. Dom then sees&nbsp;
the image of her wife coming out of the forest.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:51.840 --> 00:08:56.800
He didn't realize it was the creature until it&nbsp;
held him and hung him on the tree. Dom dies. The&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:56.800 --> 00:09:01.600
girl comes to inform Luke that your ritual will&nbsp;
begin, and either you have to kneel before him,&nbsp;&nbsp;

