or he will kill you like everyone else. Luke&nbsp;
asks the girl that what this creature is. She&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:12.000
says that it is an ancient god, one of the Jotunn&nbsp;
and offspring of Loki. Luke asks her why him? The&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:17.040
girl replies that your pain is great. He tells her&nbsp;
that I am not like you and I will not live like&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:17.040 --> 00:09:22.080
you. When the girl goes, Luke sets himself free.
He opens the door and sees outside the room.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:26.800
He then takes the wooden stick lit with fire and&nbsp;
moves upstairs. When he opens the door, he finds&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:26.800 --> 00:09:32.240
a twisted congregation of mummified worshippers&nbsp;
