00:09:36.800 --> 00:09:40.640
he looks back and gets a complete picture of&nbsp;
the creature. He tries to get a shot at it,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:40.640 --> 00:09:45.360
and after he does, the creature starts to follow&nbsp;
him. Jotunn messes with his mind and shows him the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:49.680
scene from the shop where Robert died. Luke keeps&nbsp;
running until the creature hits him, and he falls&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:49.680 --> 00:09:54.160
to the ground. The beast gives Luke a chance&nbsp;
to submit, but then he strikes it with an ax.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:54.160 --> 00:09:58.480
Luke runs from there while the creature shrieks&nbsp;
and shouts. He keeps running until he finds&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:58.480 --> 00:10:03.200
himself in an open field with the sun coming up.&nbsp;
